    {
      "id": "sybil_4_listing_4",
      "firm_id": "sybil_4",
      "description": "This vehicle is a prime example of pride of ownership. Finished in a timeless metallic coat that still holds a deep, brilliant shine, the exterior is in wonderful shape, barring a few minor stone chips on the front fascia consistent with careful highway driving. Step inside to find a meticulously kept, non-smoker cabin; the premium upholstery remains plush and supportive, showing only the lightest natural creasing on the driver\u2019s side bolster. Every feature, from the dual-zone climate control to the intuitive infotainment system, functions exactly as it should. Under the hood, the engine runs flawlessly, benefiting from a rigorous preventative maintenance schedule\u2014full service records are available for your peace of mind. It drives tight and quiet, with smooth gear transitions and responsive handling. This is a dependable, high-quality car ready for its next long-term owner.",
