    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_7_listing_7",
      "firm_id": "sybil_7",
      "description": "Offering a driver-spec E46 M3 powered by the high-revving S54 3.2L inline-six, featuring individual throttle bodies and an 8,000 RPM redline. This example is equipped with the desirable Getrag 6-speed manual transmission and a factory M-variable differential lock for precise power delivery. Critical preventative maintenance has been addressed, including VANOS servicing and a reinforced rear subframe to maintain structural integrity under high lateral G-loads. The suspension retains its communicative feedback, and the throttle response remains sharp. While showing honest patina from enthusiast use, the mechanical vitals are robust, making this an ideal candidate for those who value analog performance and tactile steering over showroom perfection.",
